# Plot of PM2.5 model and data for Nov, Dec and Jan

fig = plt.figure(figsize=(20,15))
plt.subplot(311)
sns.lineplot(data = dfmod.loc["2020-11-01":"2020-11-30"], x='datetime', y='mod_PM2.5', err_style='band', label='model', color='blue')
# plt.xticks(rotation= 10)
sns.lineplot(data = dfobs.loc["2020-11-01":"2020-11-30"], x='datetime', y='obs_PM2.5', err_style='band', label='observed', color = 'green')
#plt.xticks(rotation= 10)
plt.ylabel('PM2.5 concentration (in $\mu g/m^3$)', fontsize=14)
plt.xlabel('Time', fontsize=14)
plt.legend(loc=1, prop={'size': 14})
plt.title('November 2020', fontsize=18)

plt.subplot(312)
sns.lineplot(data = dfmod.loc["2020-12-01":"2020-12-31"], x='datetime', y='mod_PM2.5', err_style='band', label='model', color='blue')

plt.ylabel('PM2.5 concentration (in $\mu g/m^3$)', fontsize=14)
plt.xlabel('Time', fontsize=14)
plt.legend(loc=1, prop={'size': 14})
plt.title('December 2020', fontsize=18)

plt.subplot(313)
sns.lineplot(data = dfmod.loc["2021-01-01":"2021-01-31"], x='datetime', y='mod_PM2.5', err_style='band', label='model', color='blue')
# plt.xticks(rotation= 10)
sns.lineplot(data = dfobs.loc["2021-01-01":"2021-01-31"], x='datetime', y='obs_PM2.5', err_style='band', label='observed', color = 'green')
#plt.xticks(rotation= 10)
plt.ylabel('PM2.5 concentration (in $\mu g/m^3$)', fontsize=14)

quality_mod_pm25 = []

for pm25mod in pm25mod:

    if pm25mod >=0 and pm25mod <= 30:
        quality_mod_pm25.append('good')
    elif pm25mod >= 31 and pm25mod <= 60:
        quality_mod_pm25.append('satisfactory')
    elif pm25mod >= 61 and pm25mod <= 90:
        quality_mod_pm25.append('moderately polluted')
    elif pm25mod >= 91 and pm25mod <= 120:
        quality_mod_pm25.append('poor')
    elif pm25mod >= 121 and pm25mod <= 250:
        quality_mod_pm25.append('very poor')
    else:
        quality_mod_pm25.append('severe')

# Calculation of Performance metrics or Skill score for PM2.5

# Accuracy = A
# False Alarm Rate = FAR
# Probability of Detection or Hit rate = POD
# Critical Success Index or Threat score = CSI

a = pm25dict['a']
b = pm25dict['b']
c = pm25dict['c']
d = pm25dict['d']

A = ((a + d)/(a+b+c+d)) * 100
FAR = ((b)/(a+b)) * 100
POD = ((a)/(a+c)) * 100
CSI = ((a)/(a+b+c)) * 100

print("A = ", A)
print("FAR = ", FAR)
print("POD = ", POD)
print("CSI = ", CSI)

A =  88.04347826086956
FAR =  38.46153846153847
POD =  57.14285714285714
CSI =  42.10526315789473
